title.rendered: All Quiet on the Western Front

content.rendered:
Directed by Edward Berger

Written by Edward Berger. Lesley Paterson. Ian Stokell. Erich Maria Remarque

Star Daniel Brühl. Albrecht Schuch(Stanislaus Katczinsky). Sebastian Hülk. Felix Kammerer(Paul Bäumer). Edin Hasanovic. Anton von Lucke.Devid Striesow.Luc Feit. Joe Weintraub(Hauptmann Geyer). Michael Wittenborn. Dominikus Weileder(Der Junge). Aaron Hilmer. Andreas Döhler. Peter Sikorski(Sergeant). André Marcon. Alexander Schuster. Moritz Klaus. Adrian Grünewald. Felix von Bredow(German Sergeant).Tobias Langhoff. Alexander Schuster. Michael Stange

Language English. German

Producers Edward Berger. Daniel Brühl. Daniel Marc Dreifuss. Malte Grunert. Pavel Muller. Mark Nolting. Lesley Paterson. Ian Stokell. Jasmina Torbati

Production Amusement Park Films. Rocket Science. Sliding Down Rainbows Entertainment
